/>\n同上面嗰個一齊解 <br />\n潛意識常同你講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f606e7e2e41ca7e25c11150fb49394377de07e","tid":92432,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我琴日發左個夢<br />\n點解？</blockquote><br />\n同上面嗰個一齊解 <br />\n潛意識<span style=\"color: red;\">常</span>同你講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想"},{"pid":"59272c4ea6fa54e2e860b9b975a26c3a83798fb8","tid":92432,"uid":57785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:11:01.000Z","msg":"喺學校入面係咁俾狗追住我嚟咬<br />\n俾刨到好尖既鉛筆拮手指尖<br />\n係咁飲水<br />\n<br />\n三個唔同既夢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848cc9b1578a4bd224e5293b724726464b7fa9fc","tid":92432,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係公司食薯餅，仲見到許仕仁<br />\n兩部升降機都壞左<br />\n門口有袋垃圾，擺左去左手邊<br />\n兩個同事一齊走</blockquote><br />\n唔好食咁多老麥<br />\n強積金有輸有贏 唔好睇太重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n部lift同垃圾都唔關你事<br />\nlift你唔識整 垃圾唔駛你倒<br />\n嗰兩個同事唔關事 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論閒事莫理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d148ff328b2c122905b7af1dbd485cc4b3fced23","tid":92432,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T15:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個成日發夢<br />\n出街行行下發現自己條褲得前面冇後面<br />\n即係好似張卡片咁擋前面<br />\n後面個屎忽 後腳露左出黎<br />\n然後驚到醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有個d大路野 跳落地鐵路軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n露屎忽 呢個我都有相似<br />\n但我係直情無著褲<br />\n應該係你唔夠安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跳路軌呢啲關上世記憶事<br />\n自己去呢度參考<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/91812/page/4?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/91812/page